      <abstract encodinganalog="520$a" label="Abstract: ">
                    Papers of the American Methodist Episcopal clergyman, author, and President of Cazenovia Seminary, a 
					Methodist-supported school in Madison County, New York. Collection includes correspondence (1793-1878); 
					financial records (1823-1876); an autbiographical essay; diaries (1852-1875); notebooks (1856-1868); 
					sermons; and personal memorabilia, including clippings, financial records, and photographs.</abstract>
